third day
of fierce fighting.

05:29.796 --> 05:34.401 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Government forces in the
provincial capital
repelled fresh Taliban assaults,
with the

05:34.434 --> 05:36.570 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
aid of U.S. helicopters.

05:36.603 --> 05:42.008 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
