center, as hundreds
of civilians began leaving.

05:42.042 --> 05:46.346 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Local officials said they were
forced out
by the Taliban.

05:46.379 --> 05:51.818 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
