between Iraq
and Turkey, nations that have
been allies

05:51.851 --> 05:54.621 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
in the fight against the Islamic
State group.

05:54.654 --> 06:00.594 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Iraqi Parliament today
denounced Turkey's
plans to keep troops at a camp
inside Iraq

06:00.627 --> 06:02.362 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
for another year.

06:02.395 --> 06:06.933 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
