gained 112
points to close at 18281.

07:11.631 --> 07:16.536 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Nasdaq rose 26, and the S&amp;P
500 added
nine.

07:16.569 --> 07:21.007 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
