move from phase
to phase.

51:50.407 --> 51:56.847 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This might one day lead to
superconducting
materials that can do their job
at room temperature.

51:56.880 --> 51:58.849 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
