for example,
or neurological diseases.

52:52.403 --> 52:57.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And in the case of embryonic
development,
if you can see and understand
this, you can

52:57.608 --> 53:00.544 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
