there for
medicine, lots of papers
generated out of

53:04.982 --> 53:08.719 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
this one particular discovery by
this one
individual.

53:08.752 --> 53:10.487 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
